      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DUSTY PHILTRA (7) again drew a wide gate last start but did a good job, beaten 3 metres into second at this track over 2190m. Interesting to see what unfolds from this wide draw. Won't find this any harder and he can turn the recent form around. LOIERO (8) hadn't been able to find that elusive victory before making up plenty of ground in a sustained run to score at his latest appearance over 1690m at this track. Will enjoy a pretty soft run from this draw, with the sprint lane to play a big role. Tackles a similar assignment and he can salute once again. ROLLONART (2) got home by 5.5 metres over 1760m at Coolamon last start at her first race start. Strips fitter and can go on with the job. FENWAY PARK (6) is the next elect off a last-start win by 1.75 metres at Parkes over 1660m.",
